# 4EE7 - adb only - fallback
# 2d00 - USB accessory configuration
# 2d01 - USB accessory configuration, with adb
# 2d02 - audio accessory configuration
# 2d03 - audio accessory configuration, with adb
# 2d04 - USB and audio accessory configuration
